    <h1>Images</h1>
    <div style="display: flex;">
        <div style="flex: 1;">
            <form method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <label for="filename">Select Image:</label>
                <input type="file" name="filename" id="filename" required><br><br>
    
                <label for="title">Title:</label>
                <input type="text" name="title" id="title" required><br><br>
    
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" name="name" id="name" required><br><br>
    
                <label for="phonenumber">Phone number:</label>
                <input type="text" name="phonenumber" id="phonenumber" required><br><br>
    
                <label for="category">Category:</label>
                <select type="text" name="category" id="category" required><br><br>
                    <option value="Travel & Adventure">Travel & Adventure</option>
                    <option value="Hobbies & Interests">Hobbies & Interests</option>
                    <option value="Pets & Animals">Pets & Animals</option>
                    <option value="Art & Creativity">Art & Creativity</option>
                    <option value="Events & Celebrations">Events & Celebrations</option>
                    <option value="Food & Dining">Food & Dining</option> 
                    <option value="Health & Fitness">Health & Fitness</option> 
                </select>
                <button type="submit">Upload</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div style="flex: 1;" class="introduction">
            <p>Are you ready to explore a world of captivating images and share your own visual stories?</p>
            <p>Look no further! Our platform is designed to provide you with a seamless experience for discovering, uploading, and engaging with stunning imagery.</p>
            <p>Feel free to customize this introduction to match the specific features and atmosphere of your website!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
